{"tid":1741121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］律政司建議命令法庭暫緩判禁蒙面法違憲 令蒙面法繼續有效！","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:36.000Z","uid":22556,"like":10,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb45c4e38b64967e297c82cf1ac49596d4190a1","tid":1741121,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"提出禁蒙面法司法覆核的泛民立法會議員獲悉，律政司建議法庭暫緩執行裁決，令「禁蒙面法」繼續有效。 <br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（新界東）楊岳橋：「24名泛民立法會議員，透過律師樓取得律政司的建議命令，簡單而言，他們希望法庭儘管已判相關法律違憲，律政司或者政府希望法庭暫緩執行，或繼續令蒙面法有效，這是律政司的要求。簡單而言，這是輸打贏要的清楚例子，明明已是違憲法例，是不應該再有任何法律效力，而我們完全不能理解律政司這種做法有甚麼事實基礎。因根據我們理解，蒙面法是沒有實際效用，不能針對現時社會情況，作出有效制止。在這個前提下，要求法庭儘管已判相關法例違憲，仍然要繼續實施，這是錯誤的。」<br />\n<br />\n律政司建議法庭暫緩執行禁蒙面法違憲裁決<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370613&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370613%26refer%3DShare&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=6a7def5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370613%26refer%3DShare&h=0b22db51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370613&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"f5dab147f33afeda773e6ce2d3ecde36dcabdcc4","tid":1741121,"uid":274723,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"誰在破壞法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941706a3c9057f3624f646ab5b764268964d180c","tid":1741121,"uid":71770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"仲話司法獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a0a3b9fd374dee3306a41d00eebe299044e08c","tid":1741121,"uid":237425,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"律政司有得命令法官?<br />\n真係cls 以為自己係咩大帝呀?"},{"pid":"f